Description: TrueNAS network service discovery daemons
 Pure-Python implementations of mDNS/DNS-SD (RFC 6762/6763),
 NetBIOS Name Service, and Web Services Discovery for TrueNAS.
 Uses defusedxml for safe XML parsing in the WSD module.
